                    </div>
                    <span>How to Retire Happy, Wild and Free is a wonderful book. The other reviews listed here, say it all but I just had to add my two cents. Though I am a few years off from retirement age, I want to be prepared and the author has done much of the groundwork.
<br />
<br />Mr. Zelinski has been helpful in enlightening my 'field of vision' to better prepare me for life lived on the road to the golden years. I especially appreciated the quotations he has gathered to drive his points home to the reader.
<br />
<br />Thank you for sharing your insights with us. You are helping us all to make our trip to retirement a journey worth anticipating and appreciating.</span>
                  
              
